{"tid":1882998,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[A/I] 100%韓國廠驚 熱練戰士 18/2公會討伐戰 首抽決定一切 （4）","createTime":"2020-02-16T15:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T15:31:51.000Z","uid":172570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"22aafa61aad5c8d64ec7f25d72a373f3e4f0fcb1","tid":1882998,"uid":172570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T15:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxsmTAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxsmTAi.jpg&h=716b3307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzWrozP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzWrozP.png&h=a5a127fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 邊到download?</span></strong><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%B4%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB/id1480645732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%25B7%25B4%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25A3%25AB%2Fid1480645732&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbgCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=5b5d6b39\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E7%86%B1%E7%B7%B4%E6%88%B0%E5%A3%AB/id1480645732</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.superplanet.lucid2.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.superplanet.lucid2.global&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbgCffgmrlYx1zcVg66SIO7I%3D&h=b465c3be\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.superplanet.lucid2.global</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:隻game邊到黎，唔想再玩啲垃圾大陸game。</span></strong><br />\nA: 韓國GAME, 改編自同名韓國漫畫《熱練戰士》，係韓國公司SUPER PLANET出品，就算課金都唔會益到中共，好似係 (by 女人湯丸 &amp; 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q: 隻game點玩？</span></strong><br />\nA:隻game嘅戰鬥都係推圖為主 玩法有啲似epic7, king's raid個類<br />\n有pvp,但係打AI,唔係即時個種 (by 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:洗唔洗刷首抽？</span></strong><br />\nA:肯刷首抽嘅建議刷隻A+先開始,唔想刷嘅直接開始都好夠打 開波已經會送一隻A+筱蘿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XqD1TC0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqD1TC0.png&h=53bf9eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:點刷首抽？</span></strong><br />\nA:完成教學之後佢會送2張卷(2抽) <br />\n+ 每日免費 (1抽)<br />\n+ 一開始送1000石 (300一抽等於3抽) Total 總共有6抽<br />\n抽完唔啱就可以去右上嘅 設定-&gt; 帳號初始化 再入數字就搞掂 (by 百發百中)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:首抽邊隻最好？</span></strong><br />\nA:暫時都未有排行榜話邊隻最好，刷到A+基本上已經可以開波，A+係原生最稀有,比起A或以下嘅角色會多一項覺醒 = 多一招被動, 無論原生咩rank 都可以靠靈魂石升到上SS (by 百發百中)暫時比較多人讚嘅有: <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/km0Ph3u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkm0Ph3u.png&h=ffb27e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金秘書 (高攻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FubnC3L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFubnC3L.png&h=ec4b17a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萊茵 (神補，但你課夠50蚊美金會補底送一隻，唔諗住課嘅可以狗衝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKTYbo3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKTYbo3.png&h=b0cb7b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海力阿契 (神坦)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBrSfQW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBrSfQW.png&h=1e98ba84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱練戰士 (高攻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uz7x0hP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUz7x0hP.png&h=f51e3deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光明(勁，覺醒好撚型)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:普通券同高級券有乜分別？</span></strong><br />\nA:兩者都有機會出到A+ (by 老跋),但高級券個Pool應該少啲垃圾 好似係<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:酒吧右下有個鑽石符號係咩黎？</span></strong><br />\nA:抽高級券/頂高召集唔招募再抽嘅話會比返30鑽你，如果見到A角都招募啦，因為可以開圖鑑有加成。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:我想入公會，有無連登公會？</span></strong><br />\nA:初初開始玩要等12個鐘頭之後先可以入公會，離開左舊公會之後都要等12個鐘頭冷卻後先可以入其他公會。<br />\n暫時連登公會有以下呢幾個:<br />\n貓巴士 (滿)<br />\n榮光光時<br />\nLihkg<br />\nStandwithHK<br />\n黃社團<br />\nDABINLO<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:入工會有咩用？</span></strong><br />\nA:起營火比人參與同參與人地啲營火<br />\n起營火可以拎到30鑽，CD 4個鐘<br />\n參與人地營火可以加5體力，CD 1分半鐘<br />\n之後應該有公會討伐戰，但未開放<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">升等石(藍色)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">有乜用？</span></strong><br />\nA:將你人物升級，即係將你人物由A+升上S，由S升上SS。所有靈魂石都係共用，千祈唔好咁屎忽痕將啲B Grade升上去A (by 勞而不獲)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:升等石點攞？</span></strong><br />\nA:去酒館抽野，每次送你兩粒(by 路斯基7)或者商店都可以用唔同貨幣買<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">靈魂石(綠色)</span><span style=\"color: red;\">有乜用？</span></strong><br />\nA:可以提升技能等級，每一個人物都有自己嘅靈魂石，不可共用。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:靈魂石點拎？</span></strong><br />\nA:抽到重複人物又招募左嘅會獲得靈魂石，20Lv去打靈魂石副本或者唔同商店都有得買。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Q:卡關點算？</span></strong><br />\nA:返返去之前啲關打支線或者重打刷裝，呢隻game啲裝備好重要，升左裝可以差成萬戰力，升裝唔貴盡量都升到+6，+6之後如果升級失敗就會-1。附魔都可以有效提升戰力，附魔券平時打都會跌，所以唔洗太過慳住慳住，刷啲啱嘅附魔對通關好有幫助。亦都可以睇下你嘅隊伍配搭，最常見都係1補1遠2近戰。[/quote]"}]}